cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.SE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to classify user feedback. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also deals with information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Additionally, the paper deals with software engineering (cs.SE) and cybersecurity (cs.CY) as it discusses the importance of user feedback for software development and the potential security implications of user feedback.
